### 15.9 Résumé des responsabilités

| Technologie | Rôle | Où |
|---|---|---|
| **PostgreSQL** | Persistance des données | Infrastructure Supabase |
| **Prisma 7** | ORM, queries, transactions, soft-delete | `core/features/*/queries/` + `core/lib/prisma.ts` |
| **Supabase Auth** | JWT authentication uniquement | `core/lib/supabase/` + `core/middleware/session-middleware.ts` |
| **Supabase Storage** | Upload fichiers (logos, GED) | `core/features/dossiers/` |
| **Supabase Realtime** | Push WebSocket (commandes, stock, notifs) | `core/hooks/use-realtime-subscriptions.ts` |
| **Hono** | API REST type-safe, middlewares, routing | `app/api/[[...route]]/` + `core/features/*/routes/` |
| **Zod** | Validation schémas (client + serveur) | `core/features/*/zod/` + dans les queries |
| **RPC client** | Fetch type-safe (pas de string URLs) | `core/lib/rpc.ts` |
| **TanStack Query** | Cache, loading, invalidation, mutations | `core/features/*/hooks/` |
| **TanStack Table** | Rendu tableaux (colonnes, tri, filtre) | `core/features/*/view/*-columns.tsx` |
| **Upstash Redis** | Rate limiting (100 req/min/IP) | `core/middleware/rate-limiter.ts` |